---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-32 border-t border-ink-100/70 bg-cream-100/60">
  <div class="container-wide py-16 grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-4">
    <div class="md:col-span-2 max-w-md">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="grid place-items-center h-9 w-9 rounded-md bg-bridge-600 text-cream-50">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M3 17c3-6 7-6 9-6s6 0 9 6"/><circle cx="6" cy="17" r="1.3" fill="currentColor"/><circle cx="18" cy="17" r="1.3" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
        </span>
        <span class="font-display text-lg font-semibold tracking-snug">Africa Modelling Bridge</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-600">
        A consultant-led collaborative that turns publicly available government information into a living dialogue, country-led modelling questions, and actionable evidence — operationalised through a modular, open platform the whole network actually uses.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-bridge-600">
        Pilot countries · Tanzania · Malawi · DRC
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow mb-3">Explore</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-700">
        <li><a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/approach" class="link-underline">Approach</a></li>
        <li><a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/dossiers" class="link-underline">Modelling dossiers</a></li>
        <li><a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/researchers" class="link-underline">Researchers</a></li>
        <li><a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/support" class="link-underline">Funder pathway</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow mb-3">Tools</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-700">
        <li><a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/tools/triage" class="link-underline">Document Triage <span class="ml-1 text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-ember-600">live</span></a></li>
        <li><a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/tools/coauthor" class="link-underline">Dossier Co-Author</a></li>
        <li><a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/tools/coach" class="link-underline">Methods Coach</a></li>
        <li><a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/tools/search" class="link-underline">AI search</a></li>
        <li><a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/about/governance" class="link-underline">Module status board</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-ink-100/70">
    <div class="container-wide py-6 flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between text-xs text-ink-600">
      <div>
        © {year} Africa Modelling Bridge · Lead Consultant Ernest Moyo · Senior Adviser Lesley-Anne Long (Wonderfuture / Lunch for Democracy)
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/about" class="hover:text-bridge-700">About</a>
        <span class="text-ink-200">·</span>
        <a href="/africa-modelling-bridge/about/governance" class="hover:text-bridge-700">Governance</a>
        <span class="text-ink-200">·</span>
        <a href="https://github.com/" class="hover:text-bridge-700">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
